<p class="ayah 8-33" id="33" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(for) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِيُعَذِّبَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that He punishes them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهِمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) among them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُعَذِّبَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the One Who punishes them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْتَغْفِرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">seek forgiveness.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span cl