<p class="ayah 8-38" id="38" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُل</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieve</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَنتَهُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they cease</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُغْفَرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will be forgiven</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[verily]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَلَفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) past.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعُودُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they return</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقَدْ</span><s